Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:24.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}你是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:30.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}這世界的朦朧恰到好處
